<view class="page">
  <view class="content">
    <view class="icon-wrap">
      <view class="icon-text">⏳</view>
    </view>
    <view class="title">企业审核中</view>
    <view class="desc">您的企业信息正在等待管理员审核，审核通过后即可发布职位、管理投递。请耐心等待。</view>
    <view class="info-card">
      <view class="info-row">
        <text class="info-label">企业名称</text>
        <text class="info-value">{{companyName || '-'}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="info-row">
        <text class="info-label">审核状态</text>
        <text class="info-value status-pending">待审核</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="footer">
    <view class="btn" bindtap="checkStatus">刷新状态</view>
    <view class="btn btn-outline" bindtap="logout">退出登录</view>
  </view>
</view>
